genresAdvancedInfo.name: trio batak
genresAdvancedInfo.description: Trio Batak is a traditional music genre from North Sumatra, Indonesia. The music is characterized by the use of traditional instruments such as the gondang, hasapi, and taganing. The lyrics often tell stories of daily life, love, and nature in the Batak culture.
